data.description: Amazing two-story home with tons of upgrades!!  Major shopping centers and HWYs just a few minutes away from home.  . CORNER LOT!! Beautiful brick elevation, and floor plan. This home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, formal dining, and a huge game room!.  Master Suite featuring bath with double sinks, porcelain countertop, separate soaking tub and shower. TILE flooring all through the 1st floor. Kitchen includes BACKSPLASH, PORCELAIN countertops and white cabinets with undermount sinks. It is open to the breakfast area.  Kitchen overlooks the large living area with soaring ceilings. COVER PATIO in your backyard.  Beautiful community with great amenities, bike trail, splash pad, event center and SWIMMING POOL. Located in the desirable KATY ISD. This home has everything you will want and need. Stop by today -  **** MAKE IT YOURS *****
